

Walmart Sales Operations Dashboard – 

Interactive Power BI dashboard analyzing 10,000+ Walmart transactions across 3 cities. 
Tracks key metrics like revenue, product performance, customer behavior, and branch comparisons. 
Provides actionable insights on sales trends, top-performing products, revenue per customer segment, and overall operational efficiency. 
Includes visualizations for KPI tracking, revenue distribution, product popularity, and customer segmentation to support data-driven business decisions.
